All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Accounting
The Accounting class represents a bookkeeping system for tracking income and expenses for the accounting of a project.
AllProjectsController
FXML Controller class for the AllProjects.fxml file.
Bookkeeping
Bookkeeping interface is used to keep track of all the income and expenses for either budgeting for accounting.
BudgetAndAccountingApp
Starts the program by setting the root to the all projects page.
Budgeting
The Budgeting class represents a bookkeeping system for tracking income and expenses for the budgeting of a project.
EditProjectController
FXML Controller class for the EditProject.fxml file.
Expense
Class that represents an expense.

A FileHandling utility class for managing User objects by storing and retrieving them from a file.

ProjectRegistry
Registry class for all roject for auser.

Interface for a transaction.
